description: Look how he’s sweating and nervous acting as he’s taking off his hoodie. He knew they were going to see the inside of that jacket that’s why. This is Mark Zuckerberg, the so called creator of Facebook. And this lady is probably one of the few like us that knows Facebook and all other social media sites are controlled by the CIA and that he’s hiding something. I love how she calls him out💯  #hollyweirdisevil
